message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as the paper introduces a new task of Acoustic Question Answering (AQA) to promote research in acoustic reasoning. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.CV as the paper discusses the use of models (FiLM and MAC) that have been shown to work for visual reasoning and proposes a method for generating acoustic scenes using templates, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques.
